flowRoot.flowPara: frozen ganglia from donors. RAET1E not detected in any cultures, but low expression in dissected ganglia. Possibly a different timeline in human DRG, or they don't show quite the same injury response to culturing that mouse DRG do. Also, poor sequencing quality.
Thoracic vertebrectomy cohort of neuropathic pain. Not clear increase with pain (no significant regulation), but clear expression across donors. (n ~50). Largest bulk RNA-seq cohort we have.
